---
---
<section id="caracteristicas" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white border-t border-dust-grey/40 relative">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-20 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-850 mb-3 font-mono">Infraestructura Tecnológica</h2>
      <p class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-4">
        Herramientas diseñadas para una gestión transparente y eficiente
      </p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-700 text-pretty">
        Una suite de compliance integral que equilibra la facilidad de reporte con potentes utilidades de análisis interno y trazabilidad de los casos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- Feature 1: Dashboard de Control -->
      <div class="relative group bg-floral-white border border-dust-grey/65 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-almond-cream-hover hover:shadow-sm transition duration-300 reveal reveal-delay-100">
        <div>
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-white border border-dust-grey/75 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 mb-6">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Panel de control unificado</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Visualiza y prioriza reportes éticos de forma estructurada. Asigna investigadores internos, gestiona tareas, define roles jerárquicos y exporta informes listos para auditorías de compliance.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Interactive card representation -->
        <div class="mt-4 p-3.5 bg-white border border-dust-grey/60 rounded-lg space-y-2 font-mono text-[10px] text-slate-650">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-slate-800">
            <span class="font-semibold">Estado del canal</span>
            <span class="px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-almond-cream/40 text-slate-800 border border-dust-grey/60">ACTIVO</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-floral-white rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-full w-4/5 bg-almond-cream rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-slate-500">
            <span>Resolución de casos</span>
            <span class="text-slate-800 font-semibold">18 / 20 cerrados</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Gestión por IA -->
      <div class="relative group bg-floral-white border border-dust-grey/65 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-almond-cream-hover hover:shadow-sm transition duration-300 reveal reveal-delay-200">
        <div>
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-white border border-dust-grey/75 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 mb-6">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Triaje inteligente asistido por IA</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Nuestra IA ayuda a clasificar de forma autónoma la categoría y el nivel de riesgo de cada denuncia, redacta resúmenes ejecutivos y sugiere líneas de acción según tus políticas internas.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Interactive card representation -->
        <div class="mt-4 p-3.5 bg-white border border-dust-grey/60 rounded-lg space-y-2.5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-600">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-almond-cream animate-pulse"></span>
            <span>Triaje de IA sugerido...</span>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-floral-white rounded"></div>
            <div class="h-1.5 w-5/6 bg-floral-white rounded"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] font-mono text-slate-500">
            <span>Riesgo estimado:</span>
            <span class="text-amber-850 font-semibold uppercase px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded bg-almond-cream/25 border border-dust-grey/50">MEDIO - LEGAL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Trazabilidad inmutable -->
      <div class="relative group bg-floral-white border border-dust-grey/65 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-almond-cream-hover hover:shadow-sm transition duration-300 reveal reveal-delay-300">
        <div>
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-white border border-dust-grey/75 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-800 mb-6">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trazabilidad Inmutable</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Cada cambio en el estado del caso, comentarios internos o subida de evidencia se inscribe en un registro criptográfico sellado. Evita cualquier manipulación o borrado accidental de pruebas.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Interactive card representation -->
        <div class="mt-4 p-3.5 bg-white border border-dust-grey/60 rounded-lg space-y-1.5 font-mono text-[9px] text-slate-500">
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <span class="text-slate-800 font-semibold">BLOQUE VERIFICADO</span>
            <span class="text-slate-700 font-bold">SHA256 SECURE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-[8px] bg-white border border-dust-grey/50 p-1.5 rounded break-all text-slate-650">
            SHA256: 7f83b1627ff2836f32a76fef39281a8f3b2d18cb3e92c23a
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between text-[8px] text-slate-500">
            <span>Sello de tiempo legal: OK</span>
            <span>Firma digital: OK</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
